name: EPSColorSpace
shortdesc: Color space options for representing color in the exported EPS.

property.name: RGB
property.shortdesc: Represents all color values using the RGB color space. Best suited for documents that will be viewed on-screen.

property.name: CMYK
property.shortdesc: Creates a separable file by representing all color values using the gamut of CYMK process color inks.

property.name: GRAY
property.shortdesc: Converts all color values to high-quality black-and-white images. Gray levels of the converted objects represent the luminosity of the original objects.

property.name: UNCHANGED_COLOR_SPACE
property.shortdesc: Leaves each image in its original color space.
